-- Lafarge Cuts Cement Demand Outlook, Says Industry's 2010 Sales May Shrink
-- Vidya Root
-- 2010-07-30T05:09:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/lafarge-cuts-cement-demand-outlook-says-industry-s-2010-sales-may-shrink.html

          
          
             Lafarge SA cut its outlook for
cement demand in the company’s markets in 2010. The company said
the industry’s sales may range between a drop of 1 percent to a
gain of 3 percent. They had earlier said the markets may go from
flat to a gain of 5 percent.  
          
          


  


        